heimdall (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New feature: Connection Limit modal (Action Center → [l])
    - View active per-IP connection limits for a port
    - Quickly enforce 5/10/25/50/100 connection limits per IP (REJECT with tcp-reset)
    - Remove existing limits with one key [x]
  * Docs: Updated README with Connection Limit details and screenshots

 -- Serkan Sunel <serkan.sunel@gmail.com>  Tue, 12 Feb 2026 20:15:00 +0200

heimdall (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New feature: Kill Connections modal (Action Center → [k])
    - Lists active ESTABLISHED connections for selected port
    - Allows terminating connections via sudo ss -K or conntrack
    - Single-key selection (1-9) with visual feedback
  * Fixed: Connection deduplication (bidirectional connections now shown once)
  * Fixed: Connections now displayed from server perspective for clarity
  * Updated documentation with Kill Connections usage and examples

 -- Serkan Sunel <serkan.sunel@gmail.com>  Sat, 08 Feb 2026 18:15:00 +0200

